com.fdmgroup.heatseeker.model

Class Issue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fdmgroup.heatseeker.model.Issue

  • @Entity
public class Issue
extends java.lang.Object
    Issue class holds all fields relevant to an issue. Contains a list of updates. Used in User class and Department class. Indexed in database by Department and by Status to improve lookups.
    Author:
    Lawrence Leo
